1. Green wheat grass
2. Water
<span style="color: #008000;"><strong>To Make It: -</strong></span> mix a bowl of wheatgrass and one cup water in mixer Filter it well.

<strong><span style="color: #008000;">drumstick leaves Juice</span> </strong>
The third drink in the most effective drinks for weight loss, Drumstick juice, drink it at least two hours before going to sleep at night, So even while sleeping, we lose weight, If you do not get it, you can use the powder of its leaves Lose 10 kg weight just one month.
<strong><span style="color: #008000;">We need all these things to make the first drink -</span></strong>
1. Drumstick leaves(moringa leaves)
2. Lemon
3. Honey
<span style="color: #008000;"><strong>To Make It:-</strong></span>
1. mix a half bowl of drumstick leaves and one cup water in mixer Filter it well.
2. put one spoon of lemon juice.
3. half spoon of honey and its ready.
